      "markdown": "# ðŸ•’ B5 â€” Present Tense: Regulars, Stem/Spelling Changes, Reflexives (B1)\n\n**Goal:** Learn how to conjugate **regular -ar/-er/-ir verbs** in the **present indicative**, including **stem/orthographic changes** and **reflexive verbs**.\n\nThis is the foundation tense for everyday conversation.\n\n---\n\n## ðŸ“Œ Regular Endings\n\n| Person | -AR (*hablar*) | -ER (*comer*) | -IR (*vivir*) |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| yo | -o â†’ *hablo* | -o â†’ *como* | -o â†’ *vivo* |\n| tÃº | -as â†’ *hablas* | -es â†’ *comes* | -es â†’ *vives* |\n| Ã©l/ella/usted | -a â†’ *habla* | -e â†’ *come* | -e â†’ *vive* |\n| nosotros/as | -amos â†’ *hablamos* | -emos â†’ *comemos* | -imos â†’ *vivimos* |\n| vosotros/as | -Ã¡is â†’ *hablÃ¡is* | -Ã©is â†’ *comÃ©is* | -Ã­s â†’ *vivÃ­s* |\n| ellos/ellas/ustedes | -an â†’ *hablan* | -en â†’ *comen* | -en â†’ *viven* |\n\n> Ej.: *hablar â†’ hablo, hablas, habla, hablamos, hablÃ¡is, hablan*\n\n---\n\n## ðŸŒ± Stem-Changing Verbs\n- **e â†’ ie** (*pensar â†’ pienso, piensasâ€¦*)  \n- **o â†’ ue** (*dormir â†’ duermo, duermesâ€¦*)  \n- **e â†’ i** (*pedir â†’ pido, pidesâ€¦*)\n\n**âš ï¸ No change in nosotros / vosotros forms**\n\n---\n\n## âœï¸ Orthographic Changes (yo form)\n- **-ger / -gir â†’ -jo** (*proteger â†’ protejo*)  \n- **-cer / -cir â†’ -zco** (*conocer â†’ conozco*)\n\n---\n\n## ðŸ’« Reflexive Verbs\nUse **me/te/se/nos/os/se** + verb.  \nConjugate like normal and place the pronoun in front:\n\n> *Me levanto, te levantas, se levanta, nos levantamos, os levantÃ¡is, se levantan*\n\n---\n\n> ðŸ“ Summary:\n> - Use present for habitual actions, facts, general truths  \n> - Remember stem/spelling changes  \n> - Reflexives need pronouns that agree with subject\n",
